OL,3,CGovernment set to reveal details of
OL,4,Ccompensation for infected blood victims
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak issued a
OL,7,F"wholehearted and unequivocal" apology
OL,8,Fto the victims of the infected blood
OL,9,Fscandal, saying that the publication
OL,10,Fof the report into the disaster was "a
OL,11,Fday of shame for the British state".
OL,13,FThe Infected Blood Inquiry identified
OL,14,Fa "catalogue of systemic, collective
OL,15,Fand individual failures" that amounted
OL,16,Fto a "calamity".
