OL,3,CGovernment set to reveal details of
OL,4,Ccompensation for infected blood victims
OL,6,FMore than 30,000 people were infected
OL,7,Fwith deadly viruses between the 1970s
OL,8,Fand early 1990s as they received blood
OL,9,Ftransfusions or blood products while
OL,10,Freceiving NHS care.
OL,12,F"At every level, the people and
OL,13,Finstitutions in which we place our
OL,14,Ftrust failed in the most harrowing and
OL,15,Fdevastating way," the Prime Minister
OL,16,Fsaid in a statement to the House of
OL,17,FCommons on Monday.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@QO]
