OL,3,CGovernment set to reveal details of
OL,4,Ccompensation for infected blood victims
OL,6,F"Layer and layer upon hurt, endured
OL,7,Facross decades, this is an apology
OL,8,Ffrom the state to every single person
OL,9,Fimpacted by the scandal.
OL,11,F"It did not have to be this way. It
OL,12,Fshould never have been this way.
OL,14,F"And on behalf of this and every
OL,15,Fgovernment stretching back to the
OL,16,F1970s, I am truly sorry."
