OL,4,Ccompensation for infected blood victims
OL,6,FHe promised to pay "comprehensive
OL,7,Fcompensation" to those affected and
OL,8,Finfected by the scandal, with details
OL,9,Fexpected to be revealed by Cabinet
OL,10,FOffice Minister John Glen in
OL,11,FParliament on Tuesday.
OL,13,F"Whatever it costs to deliver this
OL,14,Fscheme, we will pay it," Mr Sunak said.
OL,16,FMinisters have earmarked around #10
OL,17,Fbillion for a compensation package.
