OL,4,Ccompensation for infected blood victims
OL,6,FMembers of the infected blood
OL,7,Fcommunity have said that they expect
OL,8,Fthe Government is likely to set out
OL,9,Fhow much compensation will be paid,
OL,10,Fsimplified into a few categories, or
OL,11,Ftariffs.
OL,13,FThis is likely to come under five main
OL,14,Fcategories: injury, social impact,
OL,15,Fautonomy, care and financial loss.
