OL,6,FIn the UK, corporate manslaughter
OL,7,Fprosecutions are less likely to
OL,8,Fhappen, according to Ben Harrison,
OL,9,Fhead of public law at Milners, which
OL,10,Frepresents core participants in the
OL,11,Finquiry.
OL,13,FHe told the PA news agency: "First and
OL,14,Fforemost, corporate manslaughter is
OL,15,Fgoverned by 2007 legislation which
OL,16,Fdoes not apply retrospectively to a
OL,17,Ftime when Crown Immunity existed for
OL,18,Fany such offence; the time at which so
OL,19,Fmany were tragically and fatally
OL,20,Finfected.
OL,26,@uD@]OU
