OL,6,FMinisters failed to act in order to
OL,7,Fsave face and expense, the inquiry
OL,8,Fsaid, with the current Government
OL,9,Fcriticised for failing to act
OL,10,Fimmediately on recommendations around
OL,11,Fcompensation which were made last year.
OL,13,FSir Brian said the contaminated blood
OL,14,Fdisaster is "still happening" because
OL,15,Fpatients who suffered "life-
OL,16,Fshattering" infections continue to die
OL,17,Fevery week.
OL,19,FThe former high court judge said:
OL,20,F"What I have found is that disaster
OL,21,Fwas no accident.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@]O]wD@WOUxD@KO]|D@AOU
