OL,6,F"People put their trust in doctors and
OL,7,Fthe government to keep them safe and
OL,8,Fthat trust was betrayed.
OL,10,F"Then the government compounded that
OL,11,Fagony by telling them that nothing
OL,12,Fwrong had been done, that they'd had
OL,13,Fthe best available treatment and that
OL,14,Fas soon as tests were available they
OL,15,Fwere introduced and both of those
OL,16,Fstatements were untrue.
